  "title": "Westminster Shorter Q104",
  "body": "What do we pray for in the fourth petition?\n\nIn the fourth petition, which is, 'Give us this day our daily bread,' we pray, That of God's free gift we may receive a competent portion of the good things of this life, and enjoy his blessing with them.",
